\c 23
\s Ataria anourawa, Joashi ndokugadzwa paushe
\p
\v 1 Zvino negore rechinomwe Jehoyadha akazvisimbisa, akaita sungano navakuru vamazana, vaiti: Azaria mwanakomana waJerohami, naIshimaeri mwanakomana waJehohanani, naAzaria mwanakomana waObhedhi, naMaaseya mwanakomana waAdhaya, naErishafati mwanakomana waZikiri.
\v 2 Vakapota nenyika yaJudha, vakakokera VaRevhi vapamaguta ese aJudha, navakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba aIsraeri, vakasvika Jerusarema.
\v 3 Ungano yese ikaita sungano namambo mumba maMwari. Iye akati kwavari: Tarirai, mwanakomana wamambo achabata ushe, sezvakarehwa naJehovha pamusoro pavanakomana vaDhavhidhi.
\v 4 Munofanira kuita kudai, imwi munopinda nesabata, chetatu chenyu chavapristi naVaRevhi, munofanira kuva varindi vemikova;
\v 5 chimwe chetatu chinofanira kuva paimba yamambo, nechimwe chetatu pasuwo renheyo; navanhu vese vanofanira kuva pavazhe dzeimba yaJehovha.
\v 6 Asi ngakurege kuva nomunhu umwe anopinda mumba maJehovha, asi vapristi naVaRevhi vanobatamo; ivo ngavapinde nokuti vatsvene; asi vanhu vese vanofanira kurinda imba yaJehovha.
\v 7 VaRevhi vanofanira kukomba mambo, umwe neumwe akabata nhumbi dzokurwa nadzo muruoko rwake; ani nani anopinda paimba, anofanira kuurawa; mugare namambo kana achipinda uye kana achibuda.
\v 8 Naizvozvo VaRevhi navaJudha vese vakaita zvese zvavakarairwa nomupristi Jehoyadha; umwe neumwe akatora vanhu vake, ivo vaifanira kupinda nesabata naivo vaifanira kubuda nesabata; nokuti mupristi Jehoyadha haana kutendera mapoka kuenda.
\v 9 Mupristi Jehoyadha akapa vakuru vamazana mapfumo, nenhovo, nenhovo diki, zvaiva zvamambo Dhavhidhi, zvakange zviri mumba maMwari.
\v 10 Akarongedza vanhu vese, umwe neumwe akabata nhumbi dzokurwa nadzo muruoko rwake, kubva kurutivi rworudyi rweimba kusvikira kurutivi rworuboshwe rweimba, napaaritari neimba, vakakomba mambo.
\v 11 Ipapo vakabudisa mwanakomana wamambo, vakamudzika korona, vakamupa chipupuriro, vakamuita mambo; Jehoyadha navanakomana vake vakamuzodza; vakati: Mambo ngaararame!
\p
\v 12 Zvino mambo Ataria vakati vachinzwa mhere-mhere yavanhu vakange vachimhanya nokurumbidza mambo, vakapinda kuvanhu mumba maJehovha;
\v 13 akatarira, akaona mambo amire pambiru yake pavaipinda napo, navakuru navane hwamanda vamire kuna mambo; vanhu vese venyika vakafara, vakaridza hwamanda; vaimbiwo vakaridza zvokuridza nazvo, vakaraira vairumbidza nokuimba kwavo. Ipapo mambo Ataria vakabvarura nguvo dzavo, vakati: Ndamukirwa, ndamukirwa!
\v 14 Mupristi Jehoyadha akabudisa vakuru vamazana vairaira hondo, akati kwavari: Mubudisei pakati pemisara yavanhu; ani nani anomutevera iye, ngaaurawe nomunondo; nokuti mupristi wakati: Regai kumuuraya mumba maJehovha.
\v 15 Naizvozvo vakamudziurira nzira, vakaenda nenzira yaipinda mabhiza nayo kumba kwamambo, vakamuurayirapo.
\p
\v 16 Ipapo Jehoyadha akaita sungano, iye navanhu vese namambo, kuti vave vanhu vaJehovha.
\v 17 Vanhu vese vakaenda kumba kwaBhaari, vakaiputsa; vakaputsanya aritari dzake nemifananidzo yake, vakauraya Matani mupristi waBhaari pamberi pearitari.
\v 18 Jehoyadha akaraira mabasa eimba yaJehovha kuti atarirwe navapristi VaRevhi, vakange varongedzwa naDhavhidhi mumba maJehovha, kuti vapisire Jehovha zvipiriso zvinopiswa, sezvakanyorwa pamurairo waMozisi, nomufaro nokuimba, sezvakange zvarairwa naDhavhidhi.
\v 19 Akagadzawo vatariri pamusuwo eimba yaJehovha, kuti parege kupinda munhu wakasvibiswa nechinhu chipi nechipi.
\v 20 Akaenda ana vakuru vamazana, navaikudzwa, navabati vavanhu, navanhu vese venyika, vakaburusa mambo paimba yaJehovha, vakapinda mumba mamambo napasuwo rokumusoro, vakagadza mambo pachigaro choushe.
\v 21 Naizvozvo vanhu vese venyika vakafara, guta rikanyarara; asi Ataria vakange vamuuraya nomunondo.
